<br />

<br />
Because of my work schedule I'm not able to raid much, if at all, so the hopes of ever getting a good weapon drop are nil.  I do get on for a couple hours late at night to group with my good friends.  Saving money to buy the best weapon I can is probably the only way I'm going to be able to upgrade.
<br />

<br />
I would really appreciate any suggestions my fellow bards might have.</span></td>
