				<td colspan="2"><span>The Velium Gemmed weapons look really nice, I am none too fond of the Trueborns Dagger look.  
<br />

<br />
The Velium Gemmed Mace Looks alot like the really nice looking Luclin Maces (Spiny Mace), or LoY Maces (Not the skull ones).  Never saw a Velium Gemmed Dagger, but I hope it looks like a BDMG/Gomdurig (Pimp looking Combo I loved till I got my Epic).  And the Velium Gemmed Longsword (1HS) Looks like a larger version of a Disemboweler or Wind Worn Handblade, in my opinion a really nice looking, and not overly done sword.  Nice and Basic.
<br />

<br />
Velium Gemmed weapons are averaging 25 to 30k each on Karana.  You can dual wield them quite easily on Karana if you desired.
<br />

<br />
This thread has a pic of a Velium Gemmed Longsword.
<br />
http://forums.interealms.com/ranger/showthread.php?threadid=37567&amp;highlight=velium+Gemmed</span></td>
