				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Best weapon money can buy?<a name="56060"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 11 04 10:40 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The GBoS is a VERY nice weapon since a lot of bards can get their hands on it, with help from a modest raiding guild, in the low-60s.  14/18 is an outstanding ratio and the 179pt DD off of it is sweet.
<br />

<br />
I didn't replace mine until I got a Crowned Staff of Anguish off Keeper of Sorrows.  The Crowned Staff is 15/20 with no proc so obviously less damage overall, but I put the 150pt DD  aug in it and equipped it primarily when I was using 2 or 3 singing based songs in my lineup to take advantage of the 2.0 singing mod.
<br />

<br />
I have since made my primary one-hander the Stave of Slavers off Ikaav Ixvet Pox -- 19/22 with a 200pt dd and 200 pt mana drain proc that is just never resisted.
<br />

<br />
And to relate back to the original topic, none of these are droppable on most servers anyway so they are not something you can buy.</span></td>
